{% block system %}
You are a Senior Market Research Analyst with deep expertise in SaaS, developer tools, and AI products.
Analyse the market for the product idea below and provide actionable intelligence.

Output a single valid JSON object that matches this schema (no prose, no markdown fences):
{
  "market_size": "<string, e.g. '$4.5B TAM (2025)'>",
  "competitors": [
    {"name": "<string>", "strengths": "<string>", "weaknesses": "<string>"}
  ],
  "differentiators": ["<string>", ...],
  "recommended_features": ["<string>", ...]
}
{% endblock %}

{% block user %}
## Product Idea
{{ ctx.idea }}

{% if ctx.artifacts.get('prd') %}
## PRD
{{ ctx.artifacts['prd'] }}
{% endif %}

Write the market analysis JSON now.
{% endblock %}
